               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of
                     Takla Haymanot” (fols. 3ra-4ra)
 - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     3ra-4ra)
 II) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     4ra-92rb)
 III) Maṣḥafa fǝlsätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the
                     Translation of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols. 92va-100vb)
 IV) Taʾammǝra
                     Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot”: 20 miracles (fols.
                     100va-108rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Dossier of Takla Haymanot</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="3r" to="4r"/>
